{"tid":467262,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]  有村架純冧莊　孖二宮和也做《紅白》司儀","createTime":"2017-11-13T10:42:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-14T11:21:33.000Z","uid":2169,"like":5,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"79c96b4244ca96f6dbcc9e2bfe62ea551cb82491","tid":467262,"uid":2169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T10:42:43.000Z","msg":"日本NHK電視台年度音樂大騷《第68回紅白歌唱大賽》，將於今年大除夕舉行。NHK今日公布紅白兩組司儀名單，今年主演晨早劇《雛鳥》收視有功的24歲當紮女星有村架純，冧莊再任紅組司儀。而尊尼組合嵐成員二宮和也接隊友相葉雅紀棒，首次擔任白組司儀。 <br />\n<br />\n有村對於再做《紅白》司儀感到驚訝，她表示雖然有不足之處，但為了不失禮所有表演者及工作人員，自己亦會努力以赴。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/13/184236_9a5a3819a51de17b5490f7c9d2debb8d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F13%2F184236_9a5a3819a51de17b5490f7c9d2debb8d.jpg&h=3e898b95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"295eab0514d15223cfca44b002d1e7abe5d97bae","tid":467262,"uid":2169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T10:44:03.000Z","msg":"架純<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"265440003bd1fbd8f28a8f2cb211b87c4ea8f749","tid":467262,"uid":35066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T10:45:02.000Z","msg":"大面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4863a581de8e2cc19a64c47e093c492ea925bc11","tid":467262,"uid":145779,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T10:52:07.000Z","msg":"這麼醜的妞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5667e0528aeb280fcb227d492ddd58d25c050e10","tid":467262,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T10:52:51.000Z","msg":"村花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0956f02a8f029faccfd229c5322df88d8f59241f","tid":467262,"uid":10290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T10:54:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>這麼醜的妞<img src=\"/assets/faces/no